bspwm shortcut
super + alt + t			= open terminal
super + d			= open menu
super + r			= reload sxhkd
super + shift + r		= reload bspwm
super + shift + q		= exit bspwm
super + q			= kill a window
super + (1-0)			= Switch desktop
super + shift + (1-0)		= Switch desktop
super + l			= lock the screen
super + t			= tile window
super + f			= float window
super + shift + f		= toggle fullscreen
super + shift + vimkey		= move tiling window
super + alt + vimkey		= make window bigger
super + alt + shift + vimkey	= make window smaller
